column5: Headed up to Lakair this week. Joe
What a coincidence.  Me 2.  Have baked beans, will travel.
Which tourney, Joe? The online tourney? If it's the Lakair tourney, it's automatic.

The online one.I know that they have to add people when there is enough for each team to have one person added at the same time.Art may be interested also. The Crayola ....I'm in!I think it may be my year,had a few top 5 finishes but the trophy has escaped me for some reason. Joe
It appears as though you're on team#2 and Art is on team #10
Very nice..It seems I will be slappin' fish out of Arts hands all week.Thanx. Joe
I guess I will be notching the tails on MY fish again....  Art
Just bring a hole punch Art !!
